---

## ğŸ§ª Test APIs using Postman

### Base URL

```
http://localhost:3000/api
```

### Endpoints

| Method    | Endpoint                       | Description                            |
| --------- | ------------------------------ | -------------------------------------- |
| **POST**  | `/category`                    | Create Category                        |
| **GET**   | `/category`                    | Get all categories (id + name)         |
| **GET**   | `/category/:cid/sub_cat`       | Get subcategories under category       |
| **POST**  | `/subcategory`                 | Create Subcategory                     |
| **GET**   | `/category/:cid/sub_cat/:scid` | Get items under category + subcategory |
| **POST**  | `/items`                       | Create item                            |
| **GET**   | `/items/:search`               | Search item by id or name              |
| **PATCH** | `/items/:id`                   | Update item                            |

---

## ğŸ” Example Postman Requests

### Create Category

POST `/api/category`

```json
{
  "name": "Beverages",
  "image": "img.jpg",
  "description": "Drinks section",
  "tax_applicable": true,
  "tax": 5,
  "tax_type": "GST"
}
```

### Create Subcategory

POST `/api/subcategory`

```json
{
  "name": "Soft Drinks",
  "categoryId": 1
}
```

### Create Item

POST `/api/items`

```json
{
  "name": "Coke",
  "base_amount": 50,
  "discount": 5,
  "subCategoryId": 1
}
```

### Get Subcategories under Category

```
GET /api/category/1/sub_cat
```

### Get Items under Category + Subcategory

```
GET /api/category/1/sub_cat/1
```

### Search Item

```
GET /api/items/Coke
GET /api/items/1
```

